== Introduction ==
The template should be used when a rarely-used Chinese character may not be displayed properly. Viewers may see a blank, a block or an interrogation mark. This template can provide a description of how the character should be displayed.

== Usage ==
The template can be used when a rarely-used Chinese character may not be displayed properly.

<pre><nowiki>{{Phit-sṳ|The rarely-used Chinese character that may not be displayed properly|The description of the character}}</nowiki></pre>

